########
# EPOD #
########

ePod - Handles easy-POD: write easy and simple, convert to POD, and from there you know the way.

###############
# DESCRIPTION #
###############

This module is used to conver easy-POD files to POD.

See POD for more...

################
# INSTALLATION #
################

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

